      About this item

      • 【100% Wireless & Waterproof & Portable】:Install this indoor security camera at anywhere, even without a power outlet. This small size IP camera can withstand various weather conditions by IP66 waterproof and durable materials while remaining inconspicuous. This home security cameras supports three methods connection: by home wifi, wireless or mobile phone network (suitable for outdoor sports like camping) connection. Embrace the poetic moments and distant places, knowing that you are protected.
      • 【Rechargeable & Solar Powered】: With its built-in 5200mAh battery, a single charge can support up to 5000 triggers or 1-5 months using. The outdoor camera with 1.6W solar panel ensures that just 2 hours of direct sunlight per day provides enough power for the camera to operate all day, no needing to recharge for an 365 days.You can save more than just electricity, for every unit of electricity saved, can reduce other gas emission and the consumption of approximately 400g coal, conserve 4L water.
      • 【4MP HD Video & Full Color Night Vision】: With its 4MP(2560*1440, almost 1.5 times than 1080P) high-definition lens, led spotlight and high quality full-color night vision capabilities, this hd security camera provides crystal clear images around the clock. Whether it's daylight or darkness, you'll always have a detailed view of your surroundings. The wifi wireless security camera is compatible with Hiseeu other wireless system.
      • 【PIR/AI Motion Detection & Siren Alarm & 2-Way Audio】: Built-in PIR motion sensor, this security camera supports AI-powered human detection with adjustable sensitivity levels, reducing false and unnecessary alarms. It also features a microphone and speaker that supports real-time, two-way audio calls, you can communication with your family members or visitors, no matter where you are. Smart alerts, sound and dual LED modes (white and red light) help scare off intruders and thieves effectively.
      • 【Hassle-Free Setup & Smart & Storage】: Setting up this internet security camera is a breeze in 1 min, only 3 steps by free app. Say goodbye to complicated installations. It offers Cloud/SD card and local storage options, providing flexibility based on your preference. This smart camera can working with Alexa and you can remote control it by Echo. Rest assured with our 1-year warranty and hassle-free return policy. 3 day cycle cloud storage, 15 days trial, $2.99/month for extender storage.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      • RobNC
        4.0 out of 5 stars Great Value and Performance
        Reviewed in the United States on March 14, 2025
        Color: 2 packVerified Purchase
        You get 2 very capable cameras that offer battery/solar power without needing wiring. WiFi connectivity is either 2.4ghz or 5ghz. Packaging is good.
        Let's break it down:
        Pricing- Excellent Value
        Setup- You charge the camera first, then you use the app to create and account, connect it to your WiFi and your good.
        I can also verify that the EseeCloud software for Windows also works with these cameras well. You MUST use the app first to setup the camera. I encountered issues but they were due to my very tightened network rules and MAC lockdown. most people will not encounter that problem but mine is remedied.
        Image Quality- HD mode is good quality, SD mode is sufficient but artifacts occur.
        As a security camera- motion detection works as expected with a reasonable range. Night infrared works really well and is strong.
        Connectivity in use- It will depend on your WiFi and the coverage you have. I encountered very minor lag in testing at extended ranges on 5ghz. But that is to be expected. My signal strength is medium to high/strong and there is very minor lag at times.
        The little things you should know- The included mounts are ok but not that great. They are prone to slipping as you try to adjust the camera angle and orientation. I used a small piece of 3M Temflex 2155 on the surface inside the mount where the camera arm/ball makes contact. That tightened it up a bit and made it hold adjustments better.
        It is very important that you do NOT try to insert the SD Card while the camera is initially being charged via USB cable. If you are going to install the SD card do it before you charge or after and the camera is OFF.
        The Bottom Line- It's really hard to find this good of a camera for the price asked. I've also emailed the company a couple times and they have been very responsive. I really believe they care about their product and the customer. A rare thing these days. In time their products will only get better, based on what I observed in corresponding with them.
